text: Sybra quinquevittata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1942. It is known from Borneo and Malaysia.BioLib.cz - Sybra quinquevittata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== quinquevittata Category:Beetles described in 1942
title: Sybra quinquevittata
